title: Quiz: How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns?
text:
Like 
Every single small town in America has a wooden sign in front of it with a slogan on it to welcome visitors. In your travels across this country, how many slogans have you seen welcoming you to small towns? Take this quiz to find out! 1. Please check off every slogan you’ve seen welcoming you to a small town: Welcome to Huntington: None of Us Have Watched The Sopranos , So Please Don’t Reference It. Entering Greenville: Paris of the North, Tokyo of the South, Plus a Whole Bunch of Italy Shit Welcome to Ashbury! We’ve Got Two Women Named Gayle! Welcome to Harwich! Bring Your Own Food. Now Entering Hartville: The Spiders Are Our Daughters Here. Welcome to Hillsboro! Eric Clapton Is Banned From Our Cheesecake Factory. Farmingdale Welcomes You! This Is Where All the Sauce Comes From! Welcome to Muncie: There’s Nothing We Can Do About the Howling That Comes In the Night, So Please Don’t Ask Us. Now Entering Buffalo Grove: The Town That Sometimes Has a Gas Station Welcome to Cranford, NJ! It’s Not as Loud as Beijing Here, But It’s Still Very Loud! Welcome to Eagle River: You Are Now the Mayor. Now Entering Fredericksburg: Home to the World’s Largest Cemetery of Minor League Baseball Catchers Welcome to Spring Lake: If You Drown Here, That’s On YOU Welcome to Greenville! Tune to 1420 AM radio for information on a little boy we found. Welcome to Saranac Lake: The People Who Disappeared In Our Woods Came Back Different, But At Least They Came Back! Now Entering Oak Point: Feel Free to Use Our Water Tower for Sex! Welcome to Bar Harbor: Where the L.L. Bean Is Also the Courthouse and Everyone Makes That Work Welcome to Round Rock, Mark Zuckerberg. Get results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You Haven't Seen Any Slogans Welcoming You To Small Towns! Yikes! This is incredibly embarrassing for you. You haven't encountered a single slogan welcoming you to an American small town. Try traveling around this country a little bit and encountering some small town slogans, and then take this quiz again. Share Your Results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You've Barely Encountered Any Slogans Welcoming You To Small Towns! This is a horrendous day to be alive! You've hardly encountered any slogans welcoming you to small towns! Don't you like to travel across the USA? You've really got to get out there in America and find some small towns to get welcomed to. Travel around a bit, and then take this quiz again. Share Your Results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You've Encountered A Handful Of Slogans Welcoming You To Small Towns! Okay, not bad. It looks like you've encountered a handful of slogans welcoming you to small towns. You haven't been welcomed to every small town in America, but you've been welcomed to a few. That's not terrible, but it could be better. Maybe get welcomed to a few more small towns and then take this quiz again. Share Your Results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You've Encountered A Decent Amount Of Slogans Welcoming You To Small Towns! Okay, now we're talking! It looks like you've been welcomed to a pretty healthy amount of small towns! You've seen your fair share of welcoming slogans as you've bounced from one small town to the next all over the United States. That's pretty good news! Nice job! Share Your Results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You've Encountered A Huge Amount Of Slogans Welcoming You To Small Towns! It is a wonderful hour to be alive on this planet with you! It turns out that you've encountered a tremendous number of slogans welcoming you to small towns! You've been welcomed and welcomed, and it's made you one of the masters of reading slogans! Nice job! Share Your Results Results for How Many Of These Slogans Have You Seen Welcoming You To Small Towns? You've Encountered Every Slogan Welcoming You To Small Towns! This is the happiest day of my life! It turns out that you've encountered every slogan welcoming you to small towns! You are constantly out in America getting welcomed to small towns by slogans of all shapes and sizes! Your insatiable lust for slogans has driven you to seek out every single small town you can find just for the thrill of getting welcomed to it. This has made you the King of Slogans! Congratulations! Share Your Results
